an></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Нотариус жойлашган манзил</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#5}Ҳусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-5 structure-31\" style=\"className:5 31; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#5}нотариус Ф.И.О</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#5}га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6 structure-32\" style=\"className:6 32; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}нотариал идора рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6} </span><span class=\"structures structure-6 structure-6\" style=\"className:6 6; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}-сон давлат нотариал идорасига</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мерос иши № </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Мерос иши рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Аризачининг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#13}Аризачининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#14}Аризачига паспорт берган ҳудуд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#15}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">йилда берилган</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Ариза тасдиқланган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Менинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Вафот этган шахснинг аризачига қариндошлиги ва Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#27}Вафот этган шахснинг доимий равишда яшаб келган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#29}Вафот этган шахснинг доимий равишда яшаб келган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда доимий равишда яшаб келиб, </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Шахснинг вафот этган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да вафот этди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Унинг ўлимидан сўнг мерос мол-мулк сифатида </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Марҳумнинг мероси сақланадиган банк номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> банки </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Банкнинг ҳудудий филиали</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> филиалида </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Сақланаётган жамғарма пулларининг банк ҳисоб рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ҳисоб рақамларида сақланаётган жамғарма пуллари ва уларга қўшиб ҳисобланган фоизлар қолган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1135-моддасига асосан юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка мендан бошқа қонун бўйича биринчи навбатдаги меросхўрлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Марҳум </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Шахснинг вафот этган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг мерос мол-мулкларига нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Марҳумга қонун бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">йилда </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}Мерос ишнинг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли мерос иши очилиб, менга қонун бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома берилган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка қонун бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисида қўшимча гувоҳнома беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризамга қуйидаги ҳужжатларни илова қиламан:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1. Иккита омонат дафтарча нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ариза берувчи:_________________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг шахси </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Аризачига паспорт берган ҳудуд </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Аризачининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> паспорт бўйича аниқланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус:________________________________________________________________</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 